Share with:
Production Director Job (Biomass Production), Selat Panjang, Riau, Indonesia
Country:
Indonesia
Function:
Operations
Industry:
Power Generation
Position type:
Permanent
Salary:
Negotiable
Created:
02 May 2014
Monroe Consulting is recruiting on behalf of a pioneering biomass company founded by a team of Scandinavian bio-energy experts. Established in Singapore with running operations in Indonesia, the company specializes in providing industrial grade pellets to power plants worldwide. This is crucial for developing cleaner energy and it is a future source of energy worldwide. The company provide sustainable biomass and biomass products to end users and plans to increase its supply to 1 million tons per annum by 2020, up from 50,000 tons per annum currently. Our highly respected client is looking for an outstanding Production Director for its factory in Riau, Indonesia. The winning candidate will be in charge of the factory’s production.
Key job responsibilities include:
Leading, evaluating and developing the production organization of 60 people by having a hands-on approach and good understanding of the technical and mechanical processes. Wood industry or animal feed pelleting preferred.
In charge of day-to-day operations including development and continues improvement of processes (SOP) in factory that has been operational less than a year.
Planning of the operations and organizing required resources.
Overall responsibility of production KPIs in the company and enhancing the communication between the departments.
Leadership including creating culture and forming and developing good teamwork.
Control of manufacturing process, preventive maintenance, process technology and engineering.
Develop and direct the production organization to generate operational plans to archive world class standards of performance in high quality, low cost, high productivity and environmental and social sustainability.
Requirements:
Degree in mechanical engineering
More than 10 years’ experience at a factory, preferably with an international company
Good management, leadership and manufacturing skills
Budget oriented
Proficient in English
Willing to be placed in Selat Panjang, Riau, Indonesia
All applications will be treated in the strictest of confidence.